object.name: TutorialText
object.text: These are Speedy Boots! This powerup allows the player to have faster movement on the ground and in the air. Press 'Shift' to activate Speedy Boots.

object.name: TutorialText
object.text: Speedy Boots can be used in every level now that you've collected it. Try replaying earlier levels to see how fast you can beat them now.
